  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>，並且進行火箭研究直到1941年為止。戈達德共獲得了214項[[專利|專利]]，其中83項專利在他生前獲得。

他撰寫的1919年著作《到達超高空的方法》（A Method of Reaching Extreme Altitudes）被認為是20世紀的[[火箭科學|火箭科學]]經典之一<ref>{{Citation | url = http://siarchives.si.edu/history/exhibits/documents/goddard.htm | publisher = The Smithsonian Institute | title = Archives | contribution = Goddard | accessdate = 2012-08-28 | archive-date = 2012-06-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120612043422/http://siarchives.si.edu/history/exhibits/documents/goddard.htm | dead-url = yes }}.</ref><ref>{{cite journal
